</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\]</span></span><span>
for some </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">$</span></span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\kappa</span></span><span>&gt;0</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">$</span></span><span> and an identity metric </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">$</span></span><span>d</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">_</span></span><span>I</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">$</span></span><span> that measures namespace mutation. This constraint captures the idea that identity can evolve, but only in proportion to realized action.

Second, there exists an append-only provenance map </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">$</span></span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\mathcal</span></span><span>{P}</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">$</span></span><span> such that
