Third, there exists a semantic budget functional </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">$</span></span><span>B</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">_</span></span><span>e(t)</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">$</span></span><span> with depletion under transformation, such that semantic drift satisfies
