abindex="-1" dir="auto" data-turn-id="ac76f705-9565-457a-81eb-ee1ee7876460" data-testid="conversation-turn-56" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h6 class="sr-only">ChatGPT said:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(16)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn" tabindex="-1"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="ac76f705-9565-457a-81eb-ee1ee7876460" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="178">In standard LaTeX, the entire <code data-start="30" data-end="43">\title{...}</code> is typeset at the same size, so the clean way to make the subtitle smaller is to <strong data-start="125" data-end="177">explicitly change the font size inside the title</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="180" data-end="284">Here are the <strong data-start="193" data-end="233">three correct, LuaLaTeX-safe options</strong>, from simplest to most typographically controlled.</p>
<hr data-start="286" data-end="289">
<h3 data-start="291" data-end="350"><strong data-start="295" data-end="350">Option 1 (Recommended): Size change inside <code data-start="340" data-end="348">\title</code></strong></h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="352" data-end="480"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">latex</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copy"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copy code</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-latex"><span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\title</span></span><span>{Induced Homogeneity</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\\</span></span><span>
{</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\large</span></span><span> Aspirational Pages and the Collapse of Meaning Under Engagement Optimization}}
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="482" data-end="515">You can adjust <code data-start="497" data-end="505">\large</code> to taste:</p>
<ul data-start="516" data-end="611">
<li data-start="516" data-end="550">
<p data-start="518" data-end="550"><code data-start="518" data-end="531">\normalsize</code> вҖ“ subtle reduction</p>
</li>
<li data-start="551" data-end="580">
<p data-start="553" data-end="580"><code data-start="553" data-end="561">\large</code> вҖ“ typical subtitle</p>
</li>
<li data-start="581" data-end="611">
<p data-start="583" data-end="611"><code data-start="583" data-end="591">\small</code> вҖ“ more journal-like</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="613" data-end="646">Example with a stronger contrast:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="648" data-end="781"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">latex</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copy"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copy code</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-latex"><span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\title</span></span><span>{Induced Homogeneity</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\\</span></span><span>
{</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\normalsize</span></span><span> Aspirational Pages and the Collapse of Meaning Under Engagement Optimization}}
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="783" data-end="786">
<h3 data-start="788" data-end="858"><strong data-start="792" data-end="858">Option 2: Use <code data-start="808" data-end="817">\textit</code> + size (common in humanities journals)</strong></h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="860" data-end="1001"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">latex</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copy"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copy code</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-latex"><span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\title</span></span><span>{Induced Homogeneity</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\\</span></span><span>
{</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\normalsize</span></span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\itshape</span></span><span> Aspirational Pages and the Collapse of Meaning Under Engagement Optimization}}
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1003" data-end="1046">This reads very well for conceptual papers.</p>
<hr data-start="1048" data-end="1051">
<h3 data-start="1053" data-end="1121"><strong data-start="1057" data-end="1121">Option 3: Full control with a custom title format (advanced)</strong></h3>
<p data-start="1123" data-end="1157">If you want journal-level control:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1159" data-end="1347"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">latex</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copy"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copy code</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-latex"><span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\makeatletter</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\renewcommand</span></span><span>{</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\maketitle</span></span><span>}{
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\begin</span></span><span>{center}
{</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\LARGE</span></span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\bfseries</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\@title</span></span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\par</span></span><span>}
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\vspace</span></span><span>{0.8em}
{</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\normalsize</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\@author</span></span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\par</span></span><span>}
{</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\small</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\@date</span></span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\par</span></span><span>}
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\end</span></span><span>{center}
}
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">\makeatother</span></span><span>
